pinsLabkey: Extend Pins Package for 'LabKey' Boards

pinsLabkey-package.Rd

Read and write datasets and other R objects to LabKey servers https://www.labkey.com/. Extends pins using 'Rlabkey' to enable pinning of data to LabKey "boards", with flexibility to specify which LabKey server and folder to pin to.
